{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, 10 naive models based on the previously identified features and model hyperparameters were trained and the final performance of such models was evaluated.",
    "The synthetic minority oversampling technique 50 was used during training to address label class imbalance.",
    "The Adam optimiser 51 was used with binary cross entropy with logits loss.",
    "The training utilised 10 epochs, and the model with the greatest AUROC on the validation dataset was selected as the final model to obtain results on the unseen test set.",
    "Standard ML metrics were used to evaluate model performance."
  ]
}